Charlotte Alexandra https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlotte_Alexandra 0 Charlotte Alexandra Mary Seeley, usually credited as Charlotte Alexandra, is an English film actress. She is best known for her appearance in several controversial, sexually-explicit feature films in the mid to late 1970s.She has also acted under her given name Charlotte Seeley.
